/ITThe candle is now extinguished. Some families do this by immersing it in wine from the
cup. Lights are turned on, and we continue in lively song./PR
/PR
/SCC/XXOMMENTARY/XX. Just as we greet Shabbat with blessing, we usher it out with
blessing. Candlelight and wine mark these borders. Thus we attempt to
bring the flavor and insight of Shabbat into the everyday. At /ITHavdalah/XX
there is the addition of spices, as if to revive our spirits flagging at the loss
of Shabbat and to bear the sweet savor of Shabbat into the week.    /SC/XXD.A.T./XX/PR
